        <num>CC 2604</num>
        <heading>2604.  Buyer's right of inspection</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2604.  Buyer's right of inspection
The buyer has a right to have a reasonable opportunity to inspect the things, even after delivery, for the purpose of ascertaining whether they conform to the contract.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=109662</p>
